OL,3,CTrial of man accused of murdering a
OL,4,Cwoman pushed back to December
OL,6,FThe trial of a man accused of murder
OL,7,Fin connection with a woman's death in
OL,8,FHenley-on-Thames in Oxfordshire, has
OL,9,Fbeen pushed back to December.
OL,11,FNelio Gouveia, 44, appeared at Oxford
OL,12,FCrown Court on Friday (29 May)
OL,13,Fexpecting to hear the formal charges
OL,14,Fagainst him.
