OL,3,CTrial of man accused of murdering a
OL,4,Cwoman pushed back to December
OL,6,FHowever Judge Ian Pringle told the
OL,7,Fdefendant - who required a Portuguese
OL,8,Finterpreter - he will instead be asked
OL,9,Fto enter a plea on September 18 as his
OL,10,Ftrial - initially set to start on
OL,11,FSeptember 1 - had been postponed to
OL,12,FDecember 7.
OL,14,FThe Judge said he would remain in
OL,15,Fcustody.
OL,17,FPolice launched a murder investigation
OL,18,Fwhen they found the body of 44 year
OL,19,Fold Jennifer Symonds on Phyllis Court
OL,20,FDrive on March 6.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
